name: Wife Changing Money
description: WIFE is the first token launched by HeyAnon on the Arena Social platform, built on the Avalanche network. Rooted in meme culture and DeFAI, WIFE captures the spirit of crypto-native humor and ambition. The motto “Wife Changing Money” plays on the idea that only in crypto can gains be so life-changing, you might just upgrade everything - even your wife. What makes WIFE unique is that it's the first token launched by HeyAnon.
